Home › Start Here › Canadian Pacific Railway 




The Canadian Pacific Railway
On our incredible train vacations, tour along the historic Canadian Pacific Railway routes onboard the Rocky Mountaineer and VIA Rail . You'll travel through Canada's diverse landscape including the Canadian Rockies. Marvel at spectacular scenery, plus explore lively towns & cities along the way.


Rocky Mountaineer travels through the Rocky mountainsThe Rocky Mountaineer GoldLeaf serviceSulphur Mountain gondola ride, Banff National ParkThe Rocky MountaineerGrizzly bear viewing tourVIA Rail train in the Canadian RockiesGourmet dinner onboard VIA RailHistoric Quebec CityToronto, OntarioNiagara FallsVIA Rail dining carLunenburg, Nova Scotia

 


