			VIA Rail Canada
		

			Celebrate Canada's 150th anniversary with our special pan Canadian rail experiences
		



Welcome to the Canadian Train Vacations, proud partner of VIA Rail Canada and exclusive provider of the official Pan Canadian 150th Anniversary vacations. 
In 2017, Canada turns 150 years old and all across the country Canadians are celebrating with special events. Join in the festivities - book one of our featured VIA Rail adventures for an Ultimate Canadian Experience…Coast to Coast, and receive a very special commemorative bundle of goodies unique to your route.
Depending on your route, your bundle may include items such as...


Commemorative leather bag tag, passport holder, and keepsake box
Complimentary bottle of champagne or sparkling wine onboard
Admission to the Museum for Human Rights in Winnipeg
Gift cards to spoil yourself along the way


Canada's Best Window
No other mode of transportation allows you to experience the country so intimately as onboard VIA Rail. As you settle into your seat, you'll soon relax to the rhythm of the tracks as the scenery glides by. By booking one of our exciting Pan Canadian trips below, you'll combine the joy of train travel with some of Canada's most iconic experiences:



