Trans-Canada Rail Trips
Experience the best of Canada by train. Travel from the fishing villages of Nova Scotia, experience the history of French-speaking Quebec, then cross the Prairies to the breathtaking beauty of the Canadian Rockies. Everything is customizable to your taste and budget.


Sunset train journey onboard VIA RailSunset over Stanley Park in VancouverThe Rocky Mountaineer train heading to the RockiesRocky Mountaineer GoldLeaf dome carGourmet meals on the Rocky Mountaineer trainFairmont Banff Springs HotelThe Canadian PrairiesThe Fairmont Chateau Frontenac in Quebec CityThe Toronto skyline and the CN Tower, OntarioNiagara Falls near Toronto, Ontario

 


