How to
				 book your 
				 dream journey
				 to Canada








We're here to help you get the most out of your vacation
Great trips happen when all the details are taken care of. From when to come, to where to stay, to which side of the train to sit on – you probably have a lot of questions.
We have all the answers you need, and a whole lot more. That's why we encourage you to talk to our knowledgeable vacation advisors. It's the best way to discuss the little details that will make a big difference for your tour of Canada.
This is what you get when you chat with us:

Information on the best time to visit different regions
What accommodation choices you have
Special offers and exclusive deals
What activities & events you'd enjoy
Which airports work best
Excursions and tours you might not have considered

















